o<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en Tapeten und den kleinen Beamten am Nebenti<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ch.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<lb/>Ihr <signed>Arth.</signed></closer><postscript/></div></body></text></TEI>